HEADWORD: Grime
<hw>Grime</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Dan.
<ets>grim</ets>, <ets>griim</ets>, lampblack, soot, grime, Icel.
<ets>gr⟦imac⟧ma</ets> mask, sort of hood, OD. <ets>grijmsel</ets>,
